<HEADLINE> Hawks' Steve Smith on Injured List </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	ATLANTA (AP) -- Steve Smith, the Atlanta Hawks' leading scorer,  
was placed on the injured list Monday. 
</P>
<P>
	The Hawks announced Sunday that Smith, who averages 21.4 points  
a game, would be out of action seven to 10 days. 
</P>
<P>
	Smith strained his right knee Saturday night in a 76-69 victory  
at Philadelphia. 
</P>
</TEXT>
