<HEADLINE> AP Financial News at 5:10 p.m. EST  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 *Monday, Feb. 22, 1999    	

</P>
<P>
	Stocks Soar; Dow Gains 212.73  
</P>
<P>
	NEW YORK (AP) -- Stocks prices climbed aggressively today, as  
optimism about lower interest rates and a few high-priced takeover 
deals encouraged investors to dip back into the market. The Dow 
industrials rose 212.73 to close at 9,552.68. NYSE advancers led 
decliners 1,972-1,035. The Nasdaq was up 58.41 to 2,342.01. 

</P>
<P>
	Financial Figures  
</P>
<P>
	NEW YORK (AP) -- Financial figures as of Monday's close:  
Dow Industrials:         9552.68 + 212.73
NYSE Issues:         Advances 1972  Declines 1035  Unchgd  546
NYSE Volume:         696,743,150
Most Active NYSE issue:        America Online 173 3/8  + 13
S&AMP;P 500:         1272.14 + 32.92
