<HEADLINE> AP Financial News at 11:10 a.m. EST  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 *Monday, Feb. 22, 1999    	

</P>
<P>
	Stocks Higher; Dow Up 40  
</P>
<P>
	NEW YORK (AP) -- Blue chip stocks opened higher this morning,  
jolted by a fresh round of corporate takeover news. Just before 11 
a.m. EST, the Dow industrials were up 40.26 to 9,380.21. NYSE 
advancers led decliners 1,563-917. The Nasdaq was up 2.29 at 
2,285.89. 

</P>
<P>
	Financial Figures  
</P>
<P>
	NEW YORK (AP) -- Financial figures just before 11 a.m. EST:  
